				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Small-business <a href="//www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-09-09/u-s-august-small-business-optimism-index-summary-table-.html">optimism rose</a> in August.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Families <a href="//blogs.marketwatch.com/capitolreport/2014/09/09/annual-consumer-spending-falls-for-first-time-in-three-years/">cut spending</a> on entertainment and charities in 2013.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Washington</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ House Republicans <a href="//abcnews.go.com/Politics/wireStory/house-gop-extend-export-import-bank-authority-25376358">move to extend the authority</a> of the Export-Import bank.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Online</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Today, the Internet <a href="//www.extremetech.com/computing/189539-the-great-internet-slowdown-join-tomorrows-protest-against-the-fccs-new-net-neutrality-rules">will slow down</a> to protest the Federal Communications Commissionâs new rules on net neutrality.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Thirty-three equipment manufacturers <a href="//www.pcworld.com/article/2604800/33-equipment-manufacturers-oppose-publicutility-broadband.html#tk.rss_all">oppose</a> public-utility broadband.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Google introduces a <a href="//thenextweb.com/google/2014/09/09/google-unveils-applause-hangouts-air-tool-lets-viewers-cheer-jeer-real-time/">Hangouts on Air tool</a> that lets viewers cheer and jeer in real-time. <span id="more-88473"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Google also <a href="//www.pcworld.com/article/2604780/google-convenes-first-righttobeforgotten-meeting.html">convenes</a> its first âright-to-be-forgottenâ meeting.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Apple</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ As you may have heard, Apple <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/09/10/technology/apple-aims-for-the-wrist-with-a-smartwatch-while-making-the-iphone-6-larger.html?">announced a new</a> watch and iPhone.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here are five industries the watch <a href="https://www.americanexpress.com/us/small-business/openforum/articles/5-industries-the-apple-iwatch-could-change-forever/">could change</a> forever.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here are 10 <a href="//time.com/3311862/10-things-iphone-6-apple/">things to know</a> about the new iPhone 6.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ But the more important release could turn out to be <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/business/technology/with-apple-pay-the-tech-leader-takes-its-shot-at-replacing-the-wallet/2014/09/09/587d8a06-385d-11e4-bdfb-de4104544a37_story.html">Apple Pay</a>, which aims to replace the wallet.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ And the day&#8217;s big winner might have been Denny&#8217;s, which capitalized on Apple&#8217;s <a href="//blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/09/09/apples-iphone-6-live-stream-fail/">technical difficulties</a> &#8212; with a <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/article/237263">brilliant marketing move</a>.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Finance</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Venture investors see a <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/09/07/venture-investors-see-wave-of-tech-cash-coming-from-the-east/">wave of tech cash</a> coming from Asia.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Retail</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A small-business owner says a <a href="//www.pahomepage.com/story/d/story/small-business-owner-says-big-box-store-stole-her/27069/KTKNGNSCU0eFtDt1dcLXsA">big-box store</a> stole her product design ideas.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Among male customers, the <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/09/10/realestate/commercial/a-haven-for-luxury-shoes-emerges-on-madison-avenue.html">demand for luxury shoes</a> is growing.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Entrepreneurship</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This small business is <a href="//www.forbes.com/sites/davidprosser/2014/09/09/meet-the-small-business-hoping-to-shake-up-americas-insurance-industry/">hoping to shake up</a> America&#8217;s insurance industry by making price comparisons easy.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ An entrepreneur <a href="//www.baynews9.com/content/news/baynews9/news/article.html/content/news/articles/bn9/2014/9/8/dog_fur_purse_.html">hopes to turn</a> dog hair purses into a business.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here&#8217;s why Leeza Gibbons <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/article/237117">just bought</a> a senior care franchise.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the Country</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A Philadelphia restaurant <a href="//mic.com/articles/98394/a-restaurant-tried-to-tip-shame-a-football-star-and-it-backfired-dramatically">tried to &#8220;tip-shame&#8221;</a> a football star &#8212; and it backfired.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A Florida small-business owner <a href="//www.bizpacreview.com/2014/09/09/fla-business-owner-stands-up-to-shocking-city-demands-honestly-i-feel-like-this-is-russia-144322">has been threatened</a> with daily fines if he doesnât remove a flag flying from his building.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ In Portland, a street known for sleazy bars and vacant buildings <a href="//www.oregonlive.com/portland/index.ssf/2014/09/firestone_on_foster_how_one_hi.html">has welcomed</a> a number of family-friendly businesses in recent years.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/09/10/realestate/million-dollar-parking-spot.html">Parking spaces</a> for a condo in Manhattan are selling for $1 million.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the World</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here is why the United Kingdom <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/09/10/upshot/why-does-scotland-want-independence-its-culture-vs-economics.html">may break up</a>.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Small companies across the world <a href="//www.globalsmallbusinessblog.com/2014/09/sme-confidence-has-grown-on-global-scale.html">report a rise</a> in profitability and hiring activity.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Check out 15 &#8220;beautifully cluttered&#8221; <a href="//www.buzzfeed.com/matthewtucker/beautifully-cluttered-pictures-of-independent-shops-from#2rdwxdl">portraits</a> of independent shop owners from around the world.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here are <a href="//blogs.wsj.com/economics/2014/09/09/10-takeaways-from-pew-global-economic-survey-from-greek-pessimism-to-chinese-jubilance/">10 takeaways</a> from the Pew Research Centerâs recent global economic survey (including Russians are confused about their own economy).</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Vienna<a href="//consumerist.com/2014/09/09/vienna-considering-drive-in-brothels-to-keep-prostitutes-off-the-streets/"> is considering</a> âdrive-in brothelsâ to keep prostitutes off the streets.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Opportunities</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here is why <a href="//www.slate.com/articles/business/the_edgy_optimist/2014/09/independent_bookstores_rising_they_can_t_compete_with_amazon_and_don_t_have.html">independent bookstores</a> are on the rise again.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This is proof that Americans <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2014/09/09/proof-that-americans-love-pumpkin-flavored-anything/">love pumpkin-flavored</a> anything.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Technology</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Home Depot <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/dayton/blog/morning_call/2014/09/home-depot-confirms-massive-data-breach.html">confirms a huge</a> data breach.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Salesforce <a href="//www.pcworld.com/article/2604740/salesforce-warns-customers-of-malware-attack.html">warns its customers</a> of a malware attack.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A <a href="//www.itproportal.com/2014/09/09/gartner-red-faced-after-ridiculous-internet-of-things-adoption-claim/">writer questions</a> research firm Gartner&#8217;s claim that by 2022 âthe typical family home could contain more than 500 smart devices.â</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Cisco <a href="//www.crn.com/news/networking/300073948/cisco-regains-top-seat-in-enterprise-collaboration-market-from-microsoft.htm">regains the top seat</a> in the enterprise collaboration market.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><em>Gene Marks owns the <a href="//www.marksgroup.net">Marks Group</a>, a Bala Cynwyd, Pa., consulting firm that helps clients with customer relationship management. You can follow him on <a href="https://www.twitter.com/genemarks">Twitter</a>.</em></p>
